{"tid":2295827,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭若驊：有人故意選擇性解讀《基本法》　引起很多誤解","createTime":"2020-11-22T05:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T05:40:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"5d36a2f4e0ffcc76e3fd55aa8b8179438d0ed326","tid":2295827,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:02:34.000Z","msg":"律政司司長鄭若驊在網誌表示，《基本法》在香港成功落實多年，但仍然有些人不完全理解《憲法》和《基本法》，或誤以為《憲法》在香港不適用，甚至忘記「一國兩制」的前提就是「一國」，也有人故意對《基本法》作出選擇性的解讀，最終引起很多誤解，因此律政司日前舉辦《基本法》頒布三十周年法律高峰論壇，讓社會正確認識《基本法》。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊說，論壇能加深認識特區在「一國原則」下履行維護國家安全的責任，以及《國安法》在全國的整體情況，認為有「一國」作為基礎，加上「兩制」在「一國兩制」下為香港帶來莫大的裨益，有助提升香港的國際仲裁服務，鞏固香港爭議解決中心的地位。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊認為，要融會貫通《基本法》，必須要理解它的初心，強調《基本法》只有維護國家的統一和領土完整，保持香港繁榮和穩定等目的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561297-20201122.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561297-20201122.htm&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r9xiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=041c860a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561297-20201122.htm&h=612d6163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561297-20201122.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2a9a6cfb99c9f86f25956de79dbf3c61db8cae2d","tid":2295827,"uid":36178,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:05:37.000Z","msg":"讓社會正確認識《基本法》<br />\n呢句真係可圓可點<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c27226a6fdce3816464cab7f90fafbe7746e943","tid":2295827,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:05:56.000Z","msg":"借位推post <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><b